reviews.review_text: Fatemah is very knowledgeable, approachable, personable, endlessly patient, and incredibly generous with her time. She answered every question and every part of the process clearly and thoroughly. Buying a home in the bay area is challenging, but working with her made it as painless and seamless as possible. We highly recommend her.

reviews.review_text:
Fatemah was very helpful throughout the whole process of my partner and I looking to buy a house and she made our dreams come true.  She was very responsive with questions and concerns we had.  Throughout the whole process, she's guided us with the best house that fit out needs.  The location is comfortable, quiet, and friendly.  She has been an extreme help with showing and negotiating.  The whole process was a smooth transition even through the stressful parts.  Her knowledge about the house was excellent, even if there was some unanswered questions she would get as much information and detail she can and return an answer by the same of following day.  She ordered all the proper inspections needed to insure our safe purpose.  Her team she works with are super awesome! I would highly recommend Fatemah to those who are seeking to purchase or sell a house.  Her quality of customer service is excellent! Once again, thank you for all your help, patience, and support. 
Kind Regards, 
Kyle and Rhoddavie

reviews.name: JamalCollins6
reviews.review_text: Fatemah is extremely knowledgeable, responsive and kept me calm in an this stressfully competitive Bay Area market.  I would refer anybody looking for a home to let Fatemah guide them through the process. As a first time buyer, I found it very valuable that I was able to rely on her to connect me with all of the needed experts from financing to insurance. The next time I make a purchase I will definitely call on her and would recommend her to everyone.

reviews.name: djgroupi
reviews.review_text: Fatemah did an amazing job in helping us find a house. The process was so quick. Took about two weeks in total when we really got going. She literally did not rest until we had our house. It felt like she had no other clients but us (which I'm sure was not the case!). She is dedicated and assertive and gets things done. We couldn't even keep up. We couldn't have asked for a better realtor. Thanks Fatemah!!!

reviews.name: zuser20170629124731324
reviews.review_text: Fatemah was patient through the whole process, I looked at a lot of places, put in a few bids, but when I told here that I had found "the one" she got right on it and closed the deal! It was quick and painless.  She helped with direction, but no pressure, and I ended up with exactly what I wanted.

reviews.name: user9771671
reviews.review_text: My husband and I had placed offers on seven properties around the Bay Area over the course of a year before we found Fatemah. We were feeling a bit resigned, but then a friend referred Fatemah - she was extremely responsive, available for showings at the times that worked best for our work schedules, and proactively sent us properties that fit our parameters. Most of all, Fatemah went above and beyond to help us secure the place we really wanted. We are thrilled with our new home, and so grateful for Fatemah's guidance throughout the process.

reviews.name: esunvicario1
reviews.review_text: From beginning to end, Fatemah has been extremely diligent in all aspects of helping us purchase our first home. She far exceeded our expectations and we are forever grateful for her.
